content: Yeah, I named Billy and Whiskers based on their personalities. Billy is a bit of a troublemaker, always getting into mischief and causing trouble, so the name just fit. Whiskers, on the other hand, has these super long whiskers that are really distinctive, so that's how she got her name. They're both great goats, and I'm glad I got them. Anyway, back to the hay - do you think I should get a hay analyzer to test the quality of the hay?
